distributions is nominally separately maintained by a non-context
person, who "blesses" any changes you make into the non-context
distribution.

note that this is an attempt to "square the circle" of the two
requirements without imposing an extra load on you -- i wouldn't dream
of suggesting you're not capable of doing the job.

